<h3>Labour productivity</h3>
<ul>
<li>Labor reforms need to focus on labor productivity.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Model of Japan&nbsp; = lifetime contract = <em><strong>human skill&nbsp;is the only factor of production which appreciates over time.&nbsp;</strong></em></li>
<li>continuous skill upgrade.</li></ul>
